Changelog

Version 3.7.8 (2025-04-10)
- Added 1/f plot option and cooresponding logic implements
- Enhanced validation logic
- Added file name validation when selecting input and output to prevent super long path
- Improved noise tool tab switching logic
- Reworked on UI design


Version 3.7.7 (2025-04-10)
- Fixed file name extraction logic by deleting extracted wafer info in both input and remained part synchronously
- Deleted redundant logging during file name extraction


Version 3.7.6 (2025-04-09)
- Improved file name extraction logic for seperating device name, lot, wafer and size
- Fixed debug mode logic error
- Updated noise stack and plot parts to reflect the changes


Version 3.7.5 (2025-04-09)
- Optimized matplotlib logging to only show errors
- Fixed missing minor grid in high scaling monitor
- Improved code organization by cleaning up imports
- Optimized watermark functionality in plot generation
- Removed duplicate imports


Version 3.7.4 (2024-04-09)
- Updated saved file name for plots
- Improved plot codes readibility


Version 3.7.3 (2024-04-08)
- Added watermark to plot function
- Fixed error in stacking and plotting logic
- Update requirements.txt and README.md


Version 3.7.2 (2024-04-08)
- Reworked CSV tool UI and logic funcs
- Added support for 8-inch wafer data processing
- Improved main windows ui loading func


Version 3.7.1 (2024-04-04)
- Added fallback dummy data mechanism to handle raw data missing situations
- Improved error handling for incomplete datasets